abstract: "三个从真实项目中提取的 Claude Code Skill：session-end（会话交接）、write-claude-md（CLAUDE.md 编写/审计）、kill-test-first（预登记决策审计）。每个 Skill 各经 ≥2 个不同 LLM 后端独立审查，框架整体经 50+ 轮跨模型交叉验证。采用统一的路由器模式 + 渐进式披露设计。"
abstract-en: "Three field-verified Claude Code Skills extracted from production projects: session-end (session handoff), write-claude-md (CLAUDE.md authoring/auditing), and kill-test-first (pre-registration decision audit). Each skill independently reviewed by ≥2 different LLM backends; the framework as a whole underwent 50+ rounds of cross-model verification. Unified router-pattern design with progressive disclosure."
